# Good Faith Principle
#
# Requires that certain actions be accompanied by proper notification or disclosure.
# Common in contractual relationships where one party's actions affect the other.
#
# Usage: apply good_faith(MainAction, RequiredNotice)
#
# Legal Basis: Implied covenant of good faith and fair dealing in contracts.

principle good_faith(MainAction, RequiredNotice) {
    notice_obligation = MainAction implies oblig(RequiredNotice)
}

